---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="General privacy notice for Del Security website visitors and email contacts."
  canonicalPath="/legal/privacy"
>
  <article class="prose-shell card mx-auto max-w-4xl p-8">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-text">Privacy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-soft">Effective: February 2026</p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm">
      This notice provides a general description of how Del Security handles website and communication data. It is informational and not legal advice.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl">Website data</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm">
      Basic technical data may be processed for site delivery, performance monitoring, and security operations.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl">Cookies & analytics</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm">
      This site may use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) for aggregate usage insights. GA4 is loaded only when a valid measurement ID is configured. GA4 may set cookies to distinguish unique visitors and track session behavior. No personally identifiable information is intentionally collected through analytics. Users may manage cookie preferences through their browser settings.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl">Email communications</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm">
      Information shared over email is handled according to sensitivity and engagement context. For sensitive material, encrypted communication is recommended.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl">Retention</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm">
      Retention and deletion periods are configurable and may vary by case, contract terms, and compliance requirements.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
